data.description: ***VERY MOTIVATED SELLERS*** WILLING TO OFFER A RATE BUY DOWN AND ADDITIONAL FUNDS TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS!!  WELCOME HOME! This gorgeous home in sought after Live Oak School district is professionally cleaned and move-in ready for new owners. Did not flood and does not require flood insurance. Current owner has done many improvements since purchasing the home. Some of those include a new on demand water heater, new outside a/c unit, new dishwasher, new light fixtures in the kitchen and living room, new sink and faucet in the kitchen, and painted the entire home. Inside a/c unit just got a brand new coil and will have a 5-year warranty. Carpet in master bedroom was just professionally cleaned. The spacious back yard and enclosed back patio are perfect for entertaining. Shed will also remain with the property. Do not miss out on all that this great home has to offer!
